    "longBusinessSummary": "ELCOM Technology Communications Corporation provides information technology solutions, products, and communication services worldwide. The company offers DeepVision, an AI video analysis platform to analyze and process images for identification and detection; and digital transportation products, such as intelligent operation center, ELCOM modern data platform, and ELCOM public safety system. It also provides intelligent transportation products, including intelligent transportation ecosystem; intelligent traffic monitoring, a software using Al allows detection and recording of traffic security violations; electronic toll collection; and weighing-in-motion systems; and video ringback tone platform. In addition, the company offers national defence solutions, such as EyeSea, an automatic identification system for automatic exchange of maritime information between vessels/coasts by radio; SkyEye, a satellite communication monitoring system; communication transmission solutions; safety information network monitoring products; and specialized national defence products, such as evision military system, electro optics, coastal surveillance, and UAV and USV equipment. Further, it provides CoLearn, an online learning app; 1SK, a digital healthcare platform; and VAS services. The company was formerly known as Electronics Communications Technology Investment Development Corporation and changed its name to ELCOM Technology Communications Corporation in May 2022. ELCOM Technology Communications Corporation was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
